docs {
  ## List Physical Count Detail Comments
  แสดงความคิดเห็นทั้งหมดของ physical-count-detail (พร้อม pagination)

  ### URL
  `GET {{host}}/api/{{bu_code}}/physical-count-detail-comment/:physical_count_detail_id`

  ### Path Parameters
  - `bu_code` — Business unit code
  - `physical_count_detail_id` — Physical Count Detail UUID

  ### Query Parameters
  - `version` (optional) — API version (default `latest`)
  - Pagination params (`page`, `perpage`, etc.)

  ### Sample Response 200
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "physical_count_detail_id": "uuid",
        "message": "comment text",
        "type": "user",
        "attachments": [
          {
            "fileName": "photo.jpg",
            "fileToken": "tok-1",
            "fileUrl": "",
            "contentType": "image/jpeg",
            "size": 204800
          }
        ],
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T00:00:00.000Z"
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "total": 100,
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 10
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  Note: `fileUrl` ในการ response จะว่าง — frontend ต้องเรียก
  `GET /api/{bu_code}/documents/presigned-url/{fileToken}` เพื่อแสดงไฟล์
}
